ntalk installation
===================
 
 Just type:
   % tar zxvf ntalk-x.x.tar.gz
   % make
   % make install
   
 To run:
   % ./ntalk
   
 or:
   % ./ntalk -h (server host)
   
 For help:
   % ./ntalk -?
   


 WARNING: I received a message, that sometimes ntalk doesn't
 create its configuration file correctly. You can copy
 and edit sample .ntalkrc from this directory.
